ParallelChunk.fr:
Personne ne respectera des agences issues d'États-nations; 
          par contre
        , à mon avis, une agence internationale et qui prendrait la forme d'une inspection des corps d'inspecteurs serait respectée.

ParallelChunk.en:
I see it as two steps: first and foremost that we support the Committee on the Environment; 
          but
         the same time it would make sense to go a step further and support the amendments which have been presented to the parliamentary debate by the Green Group.

Finally, I would like to draw attention to the temporary exemptions granted to the islands; 
          for example
        , in the Portuguese case, the islands of the Azores and Madeira which are exempted from the pre-treatment of waste in the main landfill on each island up to a ceiling of 15, 000 tonnes.
